---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<section
  class='flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-center w-11/12 max-md:pt-10 pb-20 mx-auto max-w-5xl'
>
  <div class='w-full pt-6 sm:pt-8 md:pt-0 lg:pr-40'>
    <h2 class='text-4xl pb-6 md:pb-8 font-bold 2xl:text-5xl'>How I Learn Something?</h2>

    <div class='max-w-2xl text-neutral-100 space-y-4 md:space-y-6'>
      <p class='text-neutral-400 font-medium'>
        Sometimes I asked that to myself too, beside my physical body is average or maybe below
        average.
      </p>

      <p class='text-neutral-400 font-medium'>
        I am pretty good at UI Engineering on the web, crafting UI that expect user to love is the
        most thing I like to do.
      </p>
      <p class='text-neutral-400 font-medium'>
        I believe user should have good experience on the web.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Image
    loading='lazy'
    src='/learn.gif'
    class='size-96 shrink-0 grow-0'
    width={500}
    height={500}
    alt='Person looking at the phone'
  />
</section>
